                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/luowenquan/">罗小贱</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2009-02-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">从学理上极度鄙视功利主义，但实在写得太彪悍了。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
